A fitness watch resting on a worn wooden gym bench, with a sweat towel draped nearby and morning light streaming through large windows. In the background, slightly out of focus, traditional Singapore shophouse architecture is visible through the gym window. The scene has warm, golden hour lighting with dust particles floating in the air. A small potted orchid sits on the windowsill, adding a touch of local character. The watch face shows a heart rate display, and a USB cable coils loosely beside it, suggesting connectivity and modern fitness tracking. Photorealistic style with shallow depth of field, emphasizing the watch as the hero object while the Singapore urban backdrop provides cultural context. Warm, satisfied mood conveying reliability and care.
